## ✅ `.gitignore`

Here’s an improved `.gitignore` file tailored for a React + Vite + Tailwind CSS project:

```gitignore
# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Runtime data
pids
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# Build output
dist
dist-ssr
.vite
*.local

# Dependency directories
node_modules/

# Vite cache
.vite/

# Tailwind/JIT cache
.tailwind/

# Optional NPM cache
.npm

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# OS files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
